<view><view class="content"><view class="title">ありがとうございます<view class="_br"></view>ご注文手続きが完了しました</view><view class="fu">ご注文の販促品は7日営業日以内<view class="_br"></view>のお届けを予定しております。</view><view class="innerContent border_bottom"><view class="innerItem"><view class="itemLeft">受注番号</view><view class="itemRight">{{query.orderId}}</view></view><view class="innerItem"><view class="itemLeft">商品名</view><view class="itemRight">{{goodsinfo.goods_name}}</view></view><view class="innerItem"><view class="itemLeft">小計</view><view class="itemRight">{{''+goodsinfo.price+'円(税込)'}}</view></view><view class="innerItem"><view class="itemLeft">数量</view><view class="itemRight">{{query.number}}</view></view><view class="innerItem"><view class="itemLeft">合計</view><view class="itemRight">{{''+goodsinfo.price*query.number+' 円(税込)'}}</view></view></view><view class="innerContent border_bottom"><view class="innerItem" style="align-items:flex-start;"><view class="itemLeft">配送先</view><view class="itemRight"><view class="mgb_20">{{'〒'+addressinfo.zip_code}}</view><view class="mgb_20">{{addressinfo.address1}}</view><block wx:if="{{addressinfo.address2!=''}}"><view class="mgb_20">{{addressinfo.address2}}</view></block><view class="mgb_20">{{addressinfo.phone}}</view><view>{{addressinfo.name}}</view></view></view></view><view class="email">{{email}}</view><view class="remark">宛にご注文内容を送信しました。<view class="_br"></view>ご確認ください。</view><view data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['toIndex',['$event']]]]]}}" class="but" bindtap="__e">TOPに戻る</view></view></view>